OL,4,G2000FStories From The National Gallery
OL,5,     GKate Bryan explores the founding
OL,6,     Gof the National Gallery, talking
OL,7,     Gto curators about the original
OL,8,     Gcollection and taking a close
OL,9,     Glook at the building's
OL,10,     Garchitecture.
OL,11,G2100FMy Week With Maggi Hambling
OL,12,     GIn this brand-new encounter with
OL,13,     Gone of our greatest living
OL,14,     Gartists, art historian and
OL,15,     Gcurator Kate Bryan immerses
OL,16,     Gherself in icon Maggi Hambling's
OL,17,     Glife and work.
OL,18,G2200FMy Week With Lubaina Himid
OL,19,     GAn exploration of Himid's life
OL,20,     Gover seven days after the crew
OL,21,     Gdeparts, as Kate captures candid
OL,22,     Gmoments with just an iPhone.
