OL,4,G2300FMy Week With Guerrilla Girls
OL,5,     GKate Bryan explores the lives of
OL,6,     Gthe Guerrilla Girls, a group of
OL,7,     Gart activists who haven't granted
OL,8,     Ga film crew full access to their
OL,9,     Glives and work in over 30 years.
OL,10,G0000FThe Black Italian Renaissance
OL,11,     GUncover the untold story of
OL,12,     GAfrican people who lived during
OL,13,     Gthe Italian Renaissance, often
OL,14,     Gappearing in famous paintings
OL,15,     Gonly to be unacknowledged and
OL,16,     Ghidden in plain sight.
